text: (chaur changcha) nowpel del puokke( tp aah hsaa b) ban mk dl puok anak pi khangleu puok anak( chrolng del sthetnow tisakheangkaet) ning pi khangokraom puok anak( chrolng del sthetnow tisakheanglich) ning nowpel del phnek laeng sa( daoysaar phyokhlach) haey chetd por penh daoy kdei ronthot . haey puok anak kit akrak champoh a l laoh krobbeb krobyeang
